nodes.text: Star Wars: The Disneyland Journey, Part Two

"Star Wars: The Disneyland Journey, Part Two" is a feature article published in the science-fiction magazine Starlog 119 in May 1987. Co-written by Walt Disney Imagagineering employees Bruce Gordon, David Mumford, and Chris Tietz, the article continues the previous issue's in-depth look at the original Disneyland Star Tours ride.
